{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileProtocol"]]},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tries to move the file or directory "},{"code":"source","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to the location specified"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"destination"},{"type":"text","text":". If native move operations are supported then this is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"used, otherwise a copy + delete fallback is used. The native"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"implementation may support moving directories (for instance on moves"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"inside the same filesystem), but the fallback code does not."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileProtocol\/move(destination:flags:cancellable:progressCallback:progressCallbackData:)-8n1cn"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"move","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"FileT"},{"kind":"text","text":">("},{"text":"destination","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"FileT","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO13FileCopyFlagsV","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/FileCopyFlags","text":"FileCopyFlags"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cancellable"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CancellableRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef"},{"text":"? = nil, "